sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Platform Component
    participant Server as NeMo Guardrails Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant InputRails as Input Rails<br/>(content safety, injection, PII)
    participant LLM as Upstream LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OutputRails as Output Rails<br/>(hallucination, factcheck)
    participant OTEL as OpenTelemetry Collector<br/>4317/4318 TCP

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 1: Chat Completion with Guardrails

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/8000, Header forwarding (X-* headers)
    activate Server

    Server->>InputRails: Process input rails
    activate InputRails
    InputRails->>LLM: Self-check guardrail prompts<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    LLM-->>InputRails: Guardrail evaluation result
    InputRails-->>Server: Input validation result
    deactivate InputRails

    alt Input rails PASS
        Server->>LLM: Chat completion request<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
        LLM-->>Server: LLM response

        Server->>OutputRails: Process output rails
        activate OutputRails
        OutputRails->>LLM: Hallucination/factcheck prompts<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
        LLM-->>OutputRails: Guardrail evaluation result
        OutputRails-->>Server: Output validation result
        deactivate OutputRails

        alt Output rails PASS
            Server-->>Client: JSON response (chat completion)
        else Output rails FAIL
            Server-->>Client: Blocked/modified response
        end
    else Input rails FAIL
        Server-->>Client: Blocked response (input rejected)
    end

    Server->>OTEL: Export traces (OTLP)<br/>gRPC/4317 or HTTP/4318
    deactivate Server

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 2: Guardrail Checks (No LLM Generation)

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP/8000, Header forwarding
    activate Server

    Server->>InputRails: Evaluate user messages (input rails)
    activate InputRails
    InputRails->>LLM: Self-check guardrail prompts<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    LLM-->>InputRails: Evaluation result
    InputRails-->>Server: Per-message rail status
    deactivate InputRails

    Server->>OutputRails: Evaluate assistant messages (output rails)
    activate OutputRails
    OutputRails->>LLM: Output check prompts<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    LLM-->>OutputRails: Evaluation result
    OutputRails-->>Server: Per-message rail status
    deactivate OutputRails

    Server-->>Client: Aggregate rail status<br/>(per-message + overall pass/fail)

    Server->>OTEL: Export traces (OTLP)
    deactivate Server
